tip.text: The Asian in me had to order the Asian Congee, and it didn't disappoint! If you want something healthier, this is a good choice to order :) Although I may ask them to make it a little less salty.
Love the pork belly/knuckle rice! Major slurps. Suggestion is to have 1 bowl of wanton mee and then share a plate of the rice with another person 😬.
Pineapple fried rice is not bad and I really enjoyed my clear and spicy soup (like clear tom yum) with chicken breast!
